Tony Abbott said the EU should 'urgently' follow his 'stop the boats' policy . 
  He introduced a military-led operation to turn back asylum seekers before they reach Australia . 
  PM said it was the only way to prevent tragedies such as the death of 900 in the Mediterranean . 
  Operation Sovereign Borders involves naval gunboats turning back boats . 
  David Cameron and other EU leaders will meet tomorrow to discuss the crisis . 
 